BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, May 14 (XINHUA) -- A two-day international 
symposium on China, Russia and the Middle Asian countries 
concluded here today. 
  Some 50 experts and scholars from Russia, Kazakhstan, Japan, 
the Republic of Korea, the United States and China participated 
in the meeting. 
  Sponsored by the Chinese Academy of Social Sciences, the 
meeting discussed bilateral as well as multilateral relations 
between China, Russia and the Middle Asian countries. 

