  [Text] At the invitation of Shandong Province, the 
economic observation group of South Kyongsang Province of ROK 
headed by Yi Tok-yong, director of the regional economic bureau 
of ROK provincial government, came to the Shandong to pay a 
friendly visit. Governor Zhai Zhihao cordially received the 
ROK guests, including Yi Tok- yong, at the Qilu Guest House of 
