encourage more ROK enterprises to invest their money in Shandong 
or to open plants. During the reception, Zhao Zhihao briefed 
the guests on the province's situation in reform, opening up, 
and economic development. He also urged both sides to further 
enhance contact and cooperation and to promote friendship and 
economic development between Shandong and South Kyongsang 
Province. 

