  [Text] Yangon [Rangoon], May 16 (XINHUA) -- Governor of 
Yunnan Province of China He Zhiqiang arrived here this afternoon 
for a ten-day visit to Myanmar [Burma]. 
  At the invitation of Minister for National Planning and 
