  [Text] Shenzhen, 15 May (TA KUNG PAO) -- Tian Jiyun, 
member of the CPC Central Committee Political Bureau and vice 
chairman of the National People's Congress [NPC] Standing 
Committee, recently conducted an inspection tour of Shenzhen. 
