<H4>    Visits Norwegian Ship Society </H4>

<F P=102> OW1405090894 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1515 
GMT 12 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1405090894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
