<H4>    Visits Danish Farmhouse </H4>

<F P=102> OW1705092394 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1536 
GMT 15 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW1705092394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
