<H3> <TI>   Hu Jintao Officiates at Henan Ceremony </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hu Jintao Officiates at Henan Ceremony </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK1805105294 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 14 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1805105294 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Today marks the 30th anniversary of the death of 
Comrade Jiao Yulu. The "Memorial Hall of Comrade Jiao Yulu" and 
the "Bronze Statue of Jiao Yulu" were solemnly and 
simultaneously inaugurated at a ceremony held in Lankao County 
today. 
  Jiang Zemin, CPC Central Committee general secretary, had 
inscribed "Memorial Hall of Comrade Jiao Yulu" for the ceremony. 
  Those attending the ceremony included: Hu Jintao, CPC 
Central Committee Political Bureau Standing Committee member and 
Secretariat member; Lu Feng, CPC Central Committee Organization 
Department director; Zeng Qinghong, CPC Central Committee 
General Office director; Zheng Keyang, CPC Central Committee 
