  When the ceremonies were over, all the comrades were shown 
around the memorial hall. On behalf of the CPC Central 
Committee, Hu Jintao laid a wreath at the tomb of Comrade Jiao 
Yulu. 
  Also laid at the tomb were wreaths from: The CPC Central 
Committee General Office; the CPC Central Committee Organization 
Department; the CPC Central Committee Propaganda Department; and 
the Henan Provincial CPC Committee. 
  In front of the tomb, Hu Jintao cordially met with the late 
Jiao Yulu's wife, sons, and daughters and had a group photo 
taken with them. 

