<F P=103> SK1405081294 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang LIAONING RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Recently, construction of the national defense 
training base of the entire people, a large and 
multiple-function range suitable for firing practice of both 
light and heavy weapons, was completed in Liaoyang and put into 
operation. The investment made in the base project amounts to 
7.2 million yuan. It occupies 60,000 square meters of land and 
total acreage of all facilities amounts to 3,500 square meters. 

</TEXT>

