<F P=100> REGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> East Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Zhejiang Marks Military Service Law Anniversary </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Zhejiang Marks Military Service Law Anniversary </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1905141894 Hangzhou ZHEJIANG RIBAO in Chinese 4 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> OW1905141894 </F>
<F P=104>  Hangzhou ZHEJIANG RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Zhejiang Carries Out Propaganda Activities Marking 10th </F>
Anniversary of Promulgation of `Military Service Law'"] 
  [Text] The Propaganda Department of the Zhejiang 
Provincial Party Committee and the headquarters and political 
department of the Zhejiang Military District recently issued a 
joint circular calling on the entire province to carry out 
propaganda and educational activities on the occasion of the 
10th anniversary of promulgation of the "Military Service Law." 
  The circular pointed out: The "Military Service Law" is the 
basic law of our military system. Since its promulgation, the 
current "Military Service Law" has played an important role in 
perfecting our socialist legal system and our military service 
system, promoting the modernization of our armed forces, and 
strengthening the reserve force. In the new situation in which 
we are deepening reform and establishing a socialist market 
economic structure, to further seriously implement the "Military 
Service Law" is of great immediate significance to stepping up 
national defense construction, promoting the all-people national 
defense concept, raising citizens' awareness of their military 
service duties, and spreading patriotism and revolutionary 
heroism. On the occasion of the 10th anniversary of the 
promulgation of the "Military Service Law," all localities and 
all units should do solid and effective work in publicizing it 
in light of their realities. With these propaganda activities, 
we should strive to encourage all people to show concern for 
national defense construction and support national defense 
construction; we should make all officers and men dedicate 
themselves to the cause of national defense; and we should lay 
an ideological foundation for promoting the implementation of 
the law and for promoting the building of the military district 
units and the province's reserve force. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-50594 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drchi097_p_94002" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-CHI-94-097 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  18 May 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Central-South Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hu Jintao Inspects Henan, Discusses Reform Measures </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hu Jintao Inspects Henan, Discusses Reform Measures </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1805170994 Beijing XINHUA in English 1519 GMT 18 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1805170994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, May 18 (XINHUA) -- A top Chinese party 
leader said that the party must center its work around the 
country's economic construction and strengthen itself while 
furthering reforms, promoting development and maintaining social 
stability. 
  Hu Jintao, member of the Standing Committee of the Political 
Bureau of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, 
made the remarks during a recent tour of central China's Henan 
Province. 
  Hu, who is a member of the Secretariat of the Central 
Committee, visited rural enterprises and villages in the east 
and north of the province during his five-day inspection. 
  The party leader encouraged party members to carry on the 
fine tradition of hard work and thrift even now they are better 
off. 
  Hu urged grassroots party organizations to take the lead in 
promoting the local economy, especially the collective sector, 
in order to achieve common prosperity through hard work. 
  Hu stressed the necessity to strengthen and improve the 
leaderships of rural grassroots party organizations. 

</TEXT>

